{"tid":1003851,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星 瑞和街又有單毆鬥事件","createTime":"2019-02-01T04:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T03:08:07.000Z","uid":38189,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b431afe180266e81fd85f2584ab6ba4e1d44a276","tid":1003851,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"瑞和街街市4食客瑣事嘈交 互毆俱傷<br />\n<br />\n觀塘瑞和街街市，周五晚上11時許，兩名男子於街市4樓一間食肆用膳期間，疑因瑣事與另外兩名男食客爭執，初則口角繼而動武，職員見狀報案。警員接報到場，4名男子均報稱受傷，一併由救護車送院治理。警方正封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190126/59186925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F59186925&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=defe4e9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F59186925&h=b02d04eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190126/59186925</a><br />\n<br />\n4個食客分別係世清、肉清、宇清同xavi_alonso"},{"pid":"bf81682285645ee70beb78b89bcf6ac46ed9f13e","tid":1003851,"uid":2002,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"世清笠水 點會係佢"},{"pid":"b47d5137584f1dedace1d1479b1439aa10ba6791","tid":1003851,"uid":37733,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"世清係唔會打"},{"pid":"d6cc552ce1eefa524cb698e6767b7ae7c8e15fb8","tid":1003851,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b47d5137584f1dedace1d1479b1439aa10ba6791","tid":1003851,"uid":37733,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"世清係唔會打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:05:03.000Z","msg":"佢忍唔到手啦"},{"pid":"10ff491301cf2b49253ccbb280da0914d94fb052","tid":1003851,"uid":216021,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"d6cc552ce1eefa524cb698e6767b7ae7c8e15fb8","tid":1003851,"ui